1
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:53,400
<i>To open a spacetime rift spanning 50 years</i>

2
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:56,320
<i>requires me to disperse</i>
<i>all of my cultivation</i>

3
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:59,000
<i>and transform into a demon form.</i>

4
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:03,640
<i>And maintaining the rift will inflict</i>

5
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:06,240
<i>continuous, severe damage</i>
<i>on the spellcaster.</i>

6
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:09,880
<i>Lu Wuyi went on continuous rewinds</i>
<i>with Lonescale's power.</i>

7
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:13,840
<i>The Oracle Stone has provided her</i>
<i>with endless power,</i>

8
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:16,160
<i>but she's still heavily wounded.</i>

9
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,720
<i>So, this time,</i>

10
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,920
<i>Li Jie,</i>

11
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,120
<i>you have to do it.</i>

12
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,800
<i>Hua Qi.</i>

13
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:28,040
<i>You must keep healing him</i>

14
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,920
<i>with the method of purification.</i>

15
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:33,840
<i>Otherwise, he won't be able</i>
<i>to bear the pain of maintaining the rift.</i>

16
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,600
<i>Mo Yuntan.</i>

17
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:45,240
<i>Your formation</i>
<i>can withstand spell attacks.</i>

18
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:47,440
<i>Keep them safe.</i>

19
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:51,000
<i>Shiguang. You will deal with Jiu Ying.</i>

20
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:53,960
<i>You're the last dragon in the world.</i>

21
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:56,640
<i>I hope you save the world.</i>

22
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:16,320
<i>Leave the rewind to me.</i>

23
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:20,240
<i>Lu Wuyi is my fated one.</i>

24
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:23,080
<i>If she is doomed to perish,</i>

25
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,280
<i>then I shall be the one</i>

26
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,520
<i>who brings everything to an end.</i>

27
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:36,240
<i>You must create another exit</i>

28
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:38,680
<i>with your own strength in the rift.</i>

29
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:44,280
<i>I'll maintain the exit here</i>
<i>with all my remaining power.</i>

30
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:46,280
<i>Make it quick.</i>

31
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,280
<i>If you can't return in time,</i>

32
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:51,800
<i>you'll be trapped in the rift</i>

33
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,520
<i>and taken to the unknown.</i>

34
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:58,200
<i>You may even cease to exist.</i>

35
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,120
Come on.

36
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:32,360
A constant stream of fear and despair.

37
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:35,160
Wu Shiguang. How are you going to beat me?

38
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:22,200
With your twin blades unsheathed,

39
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:27,200
this empty chest of yours
is as vulnerable as a sheet of paper.

40
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:54,520
Hua Qi, don't be distracted.

41
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:56,040
Keep healing Li Jie.

42
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,880
The earthquake

43
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,080
stopped.

44
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:45,800
Wu Wangyan is still so silly.

45
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:48,040
What did you say?

46
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,800
Why do you think
the Four-Pillar Formation stopped?

47
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:55,680
Because they sacrificed themselves.

48
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:56,560
Jin Zheng.

49
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,360
My soul I devote.

50
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,560
Long live the dragon.

51
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,240
Mo Yuntan. No!

52
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:24,800
<i>You annoying junior.</i>

53
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:28,320
Hurry up and become a double-flower.

54
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:31,960
Congratulations on becoming
a double-flower.

55
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:41,040
Cherish me.

56
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:43,200
Only I would call you Senior.

57
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:10,120
<i>You must create another exit</i>

58
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:12,560
<i>with your own strength in the rift.</i>

59
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:16,480
<i>Although you have</i>
<i>the Dragon Deity's Power of Chi Wen,</i>

60
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:19,240
<i>you can't reach</i>
<i>the realm of the six-flower yet.</i>

61
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,920
<i>Just do your best.</i>

62
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:47,120
Wrathful sandstorm.

63
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:56,280
Eastern Purple Lightning.

64
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,600
Searing flames.

65
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,880
By the fox's call.

66
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:03,560
Rewind of Sun and Moon.

67
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:13,800
Grant me your power.

68
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:19,080
<i>Master Ji Ling.</i>

69
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:21,080
<i>From now on,</i>

70
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:23,240
<i>you're on your own.</i>

71
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:29,440
Come!

72
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,960
How dare you trespass
into the Formless Moon?

73
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:39,120
Who are you?

74
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:48,440
The man who came to take your life.

75
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:23,160
Ji Ling.

76
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:33,320
Where is Ji Ling?

77
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:35,400
Lu Wuyi.

78
00:17:09,119 --> 00:17:10,560
Use the Guili Sword

79
00:17:11,599 --> 00:17:13,160
and the Dragon Deity's Power

80
00:17:14,359 --> 00:17:16,800
to destroy the last shard
of the Oracle Stone.

81
00:17:17,839 --> 00:17:19,119
Only then

82
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:24,280
can you kill Jiu Ying for good.

83
00:17:25,359 --> 00:17:27,400
But you'll also die.

84
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:37,160
I was never supposed to exist.

85
00:17:42,560 --> 00:17:43,720
Wu Shiguang.

86
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:47,400
Tell Wangyan

87
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,320
that I miss her.

88
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:48,600
No.

89
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:51,640
You're dying with me.

90
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:07,880
Ji Ling.

91
00:19:37,560 --> 00:19:38,640
Ji Ling.

92
00:19:41,360 --> 00:19:42,920
I'm coming to you.

93
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:45,920
Don't cry.

94
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:47,760
Ji…

95
00:19:47,840 --> 00:19:48,880
Don't cry.

96
00:19:49,800 --> 00:19:51,440
I'll wait for you over there.

97
00:19:52,760 --> 00:19:55,680
I'll pick you up with a bundle of flowers.

98
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:59,000
A huge bundle.

99
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:01,600
This way,

100
00:20:03,240 --> 00:20:05,240
you won't be afraid.

101
00:20:07,320 --> 00:20:09,840
Remember to pick me up with flowers.

102
00:20:12,320 --> 00:20:14,680
I want a huge bundle of flowers.

103
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:41,360
Who are you?

104
00:21:48,040 --> 00:21:49,400
Where am I?

105
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:00,240
Are you also

106
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,160
going to kill me?

107
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:09,120
I've been looking for you.

108
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:12,000
I'll take you home.

109
00:22:18,760 --> 00:22:19,920
I'm scared.

110
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:23,280
Of me?

111
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:31,760
Of this place.

112
00:22:32,360 --> 00:22:33,440
It's so dark

113
00:22:34,560 --> 00:22:35,560
and so cold.

114
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:40,320
But I don't know why

115
00:22:42,880 --> 00:22:44,240
I feel at ease

116
00:22:46,040 --> 00:22:47,560
looking at you.

117
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:03,000
Then just look at me.

118
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:04,840
This way,

119
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:07,320
you won't be afraid.

120
00:23:11,320 --> 00:23:13,280
I think I'm really not afraid anymore.

121
00:23:18,560 --> 00:23:20,200
What's your name?

122
00:23:23,800 --> 00:23:24,800
My name

123
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:29,080
is Ji Ling.

124
00:23:31,040 --> 00:23:32,920
"Ji" as in "a temporary lodging".

125
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:35,920
"Ling" as in "hearts connected".

126
00:23:42,080 --> 00:23:44,160
Ji Ling.

127
00:23:48,280 --> 00:23:49,680
I'll remember it.

128
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:05,400
Go to sleep.

129
00:24:54,360 --> 00:24:55,240
Li Jie.

130
00:24:58,640 --> 00:24:59,760
Master Dragon Deity.

131
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:06,840
Master Dragon Deity.

132
00:25:08,760 --> 00:25:09,760
Master Dragon Deity.

133
00:25:09,840 --> 00:25:11,160
We did it.

134
00:25:12,160 --> 00:25:13,520
We did it.

135
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:16,280
-Master Dragon Deity.
-We did it.

136
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:18,520
Thank you.

137
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,080
Thank you all.

138
00:25:23,400 --> 00:25:24,240
Thank you.

139
00:25:53,240 --> 00:25:54,120
Don't be sad.

140
00:25:55,360 --> 00:25:57,920
Maybe they just went to another world.

141
00:25:59,920 --> 00:26:01,200
Or perhaps,

142
00:26:01,800 --> 00:26:04,720
Ji Ling chose to stay
in the spacetime rift.

143
00:26:05,520 --> 00:26:07,760
I bet he didn't want to come back

144
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:11,600
to this world where Lu Wuyi never existed.

145
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:31,480
Wu Wangyan.

146
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:33,360
You Chi.

147
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:35,800
Wu Wangyan.

148
00:27:36,320 --> 00:27:38,280
I always called you a coward

149
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:40,840
who runs away from danger.

150
00:27:41,360 --> 00:27:42,680
Why didn't you run?

151
00:27:49,120 --> 00:27:50,520
Why didn't you run?

152
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:53,000
Why didn't you run?

153
00:29:05,880 --> 00:29:07,080
Wu Shiguang.

154
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:10,640
In this life,

155
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:14,040
I can't repay

156
00:29:17,840 --> 00:29:19,240
your deep affection.

157
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:22,760
If there is an afterlife,

158
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,880
I swear I will find you.

159
00:29:42,560 --> 00:29:44,280
Please save my sister.

160
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:20,880
Are you scared?

161
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:26,200
No.

162
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:49,520
Morning, Master Dragon Deity.

163
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,200
Master Dragon Deity.

164
00:33:56,600 --> 00:33:57,640
Wu Shiguang.

165
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:00,840
What are you doing here?

166
00:34:52,719 --> 00:34:53,719
What's wrong?

167
00:35:03,240 --> 00:35:04,920
What happened to your face?

168
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,760
Got into a fight again?

169
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:13,920
I've been busy these days.

170
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:17,080
Being a commander of the Shilin Sect

171
00:35:17,160 --> 00:35:19,080
is harder than I thought.

172
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:21,200
But Father always said,

173
00:35:21,760 --> 00:35:23,560
"Do your best."

174
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:28,240
Work harder.

175
00:35:31,680 --> 00:35:35,160
You've always been such a crybaby.

176
00:35:35,240 --> 00:35:37,200
You're the Master Dragon Deity now.

177
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:39,600
You can't be
that scared little boy anymore.

178
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:05,640
What's wrong? Had a nightmare?

179
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:08,600
No.

180
00:36:10,560 --> 00:36:12,080
It was a sweet dream.

181
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:19,840
But then I woke up.

182
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:23,600
So, I'm a bit upset.

183
00:36:26,440 --> 00:36:28,040
I came to tell you

184
00:36:28,680 --> 00:36:30,960
that the Oracle Stone gave a new prophecy.

185
00:36:33,240 --> 00:36:34,200
The old dragon falls.

186
00:36:34,720 --> 00:36:35,920
The new dragon rises.

187
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:37,840
Rewind the river of time.

188
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:39,880
A new chapter has started.

189
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:51,120
-Master Dragon Deity.
-We pray for your blessings.

190
00:36:51,200 --> 00:36:52,560
Master Dragon Deity, please…

191
00:36:52,640 --> 00:36:54,080
-Please grant my wishes.
-Master Dragon Deity…

192
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:59,120
ALL FLOURISH FOR THE SCALES

193
00:36:59,200 --> 00:37:01,560
SERVE THE SCALES, UPHOLD THE RIGHT

194
00:37:01,640 --> 00:37:03,400
You've become the Master Dragon Deity.

195
00:37:04,160 --> 00:37:05,200
I have to work harder

196
00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:08,960
to be a great hero
and honor our ancestors.

197
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:16,880
You're already a great hero.

198
00:37:19,600 --> 00:37:20,480
Again?

199
00:37:21,080 --> 00:37:22,200
Father once said,

200
00:37:23,240 --> 00:37:24,320
"Be down to earth.

201
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:26,480
Stop daydreaming."

202
00:37:40,920 --> 00:37:41,920
Miss Mu Long.

203
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:47,320
You came to offer incense too?

204
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:51,600
I finished my book.

205
00:37:52,440 --> 00:37:54,120
Want to read it?

206
00:37:55,560 --> 00:37:56,960
O-Of course.

207
00:37:57,040 --> 00:37:58,160
I want to be your first…

208
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:02,080
first reader.

209
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:07,080
TALES TOLD BY MU, MU LONG

210
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:28,520
Brother. Do you have any coins?

211
00:38:28,600 --> 00:38:32,280
Can I get a coin
for the Pond of Merit to make a wish?

212
00:38:40,160 --> 00:38:42,600
Master Dragon Deity will keep blessing us.

213
00:38:43,680 --> 00:38:45,080
Look, a double-flower hunter.

214
00:38:45,160 --> 00:38:46,960
I saw a double-flower hunter.

215
00:38:47,040 --> 00:38:48,960
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

216
00:38:53,800 --> 00:38:55,760
I saw a double-flower hunter.

217
00:38:55,840 --> 00:38:58,040
The middle one has one more flower.

218
00:38:58,120 --> 00:38:59,320
Triple-flower.

219
00:38:59,400 --> 00:39:00,640
Triple-flower.

220
00:39:00,720 --> 00:39:01,960
Come and see!

221
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:03,920
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

222
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:05,680
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

223
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:07,560
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

224
00:39:07,640 --> 00:39:09,000
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

225
00:39:09,080 --> 00:39:10,960
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

226
00:39:19,720 --> 00:39:20,680
<i>Ji Ling.</i>

227
00:39:21,520 --> 00:39:22,520
<i>Do you see it?</i>

228
00:39:23,640 --> 00:39:26,360
<i>It's the wonderful world</i>
<i>you died to protect.</i>

229
00:39:28,640 --> 00:39:30,280
<i>I'll keep guarding it.</i>

230
00:39:31,640 --> 00:39:33,360
<i>As long as there are dragons,</i>

231
00:39:34,240 --> 00:39:37,480
<i>the light of faith</i>
<i>will not be extinguished.</i>

232
00:39:51,120 --> 00:39:52,320
Wu Wangyan.

233
00:40:11,120 --> 00:40:12,240
You are…

234
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:42,480
Why do you have my hair?

235
00:40:50,600 --> 00:40:51,840
That is

236
00:40:54,040 --> 00:40:57,560
a long story to be told.

237
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:24,640
<i>Once,</i>

238
00:41:24,720 --> 00:41:27,200
<i>I thought the mission was everything,</i>

239
00:41:27,880 --> 00:41:31,160
<i>but I never thought that the mission</i>
<i>would come to an end.</i>

240
00:41:32,240 --> 00:41:34,360
<i>Maybe it's time to let go</i>

241
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:37,240
<i>and see the world out there.</i>

242
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:41,560
<i>Maybe I'll figure out who I am</i>

243
00:41:42,280 --> 00:41:44,360
<i>and the meaning of my existence.</i>

244
00:41:45,200 --> 00:41:47,640
<i>And this is probably the answer</i>

245
00:41:48,200 --> 00:41:49,760
<i>all of us</i>

246
00:41:50,280 --> 00:41:52,240
<i>are seeking our entire lives.</i>

247
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:54,880
<i>Come and find me.</i>

248
00:41:57,960 --> 00:42:01,360
<i>And I think there is a voice</i>

249
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:03,280
<i>telling me to find someone.</i>

250
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:05,600
<i>But I don't know</i>
<i>where to find that person.</i>

251
00:42:05,680 --> 00:42:08,160
<i>I don't even know his name.</i>

252
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:15,800
MOONLIGHT OVER THE WASTELAND
SCALES BLESS ALL CREATURES

253
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:18,680
GORGEOUS AS A DREAM
FATE'S PATHS CONVERGE

254
00:42:28,120 --> 00:42:30,600
Demons coming!

255
00:42:30,680 --> 00:42:33,320
Demons coming!

256
00:42:33,400 --> 00:42:35,280
-Here to catch you.
-Be careful.

257
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:36,320
Come here.

258
00:42:37,520 --> 00:42:39,880
There are no demons in the world.

259
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:43,400
Those are stories adults made up
to scare the kids.

260
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:45,600
How boring.

261
00:42:45,680 --> 00:42:48,040
It would be so much fun

262
00:42:48,120 --> 00:42:49,440
if there were demons.

263
00:42:50,600 --> 00:42:51,440
Here.

264
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:54,480
Demons coming!

265
00:42:54,560 --> 00:42:56,160
Demons coming to catch you!

266
00:42:56,240 --> 00:42:57,720
Demons coming to catch you!

267
00:42:58,240 --> 00:42:59,320
Demons coming!

268
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:01,080
Here to catch you!

269
00:43:01,160 --> 00:43:06,600
PETALS AND GREENS

270
00:44:04,320 --> 00:44:05,960
Young Miss, do you like flowers?

271
00:44:10,640 --> 00:44:11,480
Yes, I do.

272
00:44:12,560 --> 00:44:13,480
Would you like some?

273
00:44:16,720 --> 00:44:18,400
All fresh. I just picked them.

274
00:44:20,880 --> 00:44:21,720
I…

275
00:44:23,360 --> 00:44:24,360
have no money.

276
00:44:29,640 --> 00:44:31,440
I'm just a worker here.

277
00:44:31,960 --> 00:44:33,720
If I were the boss,

278
00:44:34,400 --> 00:44:36,120
I would give you some.

279
00:44:36,200 --> 00:44:37,760
What should I do?

280
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:39,960
No need.

281
00:44:40,480 --> 00:44:42,920
You don't have to do this. Thank you.

282
00:45:01,640 --> 00:45:02,520
Young Miss.

283
00:45:24,080 --> 00:45:25,120
Here.

284
00:45:38,720 --> 00:45:40,600
You… You don't want them?

285
00:45:41,440 --> 00:45:44,440
I picked these raspberries
by the lake near home.

286
00:45:44,520 --> 00:45:47,080
Do… Do you like raspberries?

287
00:46:16,880 --> 00:46:17,920
So sweet.

